				<wikidot:authorName>DrCaroll</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3828846</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>The creepypasta feel is exactly what I was going for. The original addition I tried to implement is that they don’t mean any harm, nor do they just sit back and watch people, giving them the creeps. They are just trying to comfort people in any way to get them in a better place than they are now.</p> 
				 	]]>
