				<wikidot:authorName>DrCaroll</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3828846</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Well, just about anything with moveable limbs can snap a neck. While, yes, the sharp parts of SCP-4655-1’s limbs wouldn’t be able to get a good grip on the mother’s head, it could simply get a grasp of her with holding just a bit further down its arms with the more broad area that doesn’t end in a point.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
