				<wikidot:authorName>DrCaroll</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3828846</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <div style="text-align: center;"> <p><strong><em>They're just here to help.</em></strong></p> </div> <br /> My first attempt at a truly creepy skip. I hope I managed to give you all some chills, or at least some goosebumps. <p>Credit as due: thank you to #thecritters user <em>PopcornK</em>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/notexactlyhuman" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3143506&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1550712885" alt="Notexactlyhuman" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3143506)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/notexactlyhuman" >Notexactlyhuman</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rounderhouse" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4187885&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1550712885" alt="Rounderhouse" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4187885)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rounderhouse" >Rounderhouse</a></span> for critique!</p> <p>But more importantly, thank <em>you</em> for reading.</p> <p>Check out some of my other works <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/researcher-caroll-s-personnel-file">here!</a></p> <p>Note: the lack of the nu-SCP theme for this article despite all of the ones I've written before having it is intentional. I feel the regular theme fits the feel of the article better.</p> 
				 	]]>
